    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is, ideally for parts or as a major restoration project. The engine currently struggles to start and requires significant mechanical attention, while the body shows extensive rust, several dents, and faded paint throughout. Inside, the interior is heavily worn with torn upholstery and non-functioning electronics, making it a challenging but potentially rewarding project for the right buyer.",
